世界最大的[[罂粟籽|罂粟籽]]生产国为[[捷克共和国|捷克共和国]]<ref name=faostat16/>，主要进口国为[[印度|印度]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[波兰|波兰]]和[[德国|德国]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sergeeva |first1=Anna |title=Global Poppy Seed Market - The Czech Republic Is the Key Producing Country |url=https://www.indexbox.io/blog/global-poppy-seed-market/ |website=Index Box |publisher=Index Box |accessdate=15 November 2018 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412104501/https://www.indexbox.io/blog/global-poppy-seed-market/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

全世界最大的[[海洛因|海洛因]]产地[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]也种植有大量罂粟<ref name="#1">{{cite AV media|people=David Greene (host, Morning Edition), Hayatullah Hayat (Governor of Helmand Province, Afghanistan), Tom Bowman (reporter), Dianne Feinstein (U.S. Senator, Chair of the Caucus on International Narcotics Control)|date=6 July 2016|title=Afghan Governor Wants Government To Control Poppy Crop|medium=Radio broadcast|url=https://www.npr.org/2016/07/06/484894669/afghan-governor-wants-government-to-control-poppy-crop|access-date=6 July 2016|time=0:10|publisher=NPR|quote=Afghanistan's poppy production… accounts for more than 91 percent of the world's heroin.|archive-date=2016-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160707155533/http://www.npr.org/2016/07/06/484894669/afghan-governor-wants-government-to-control-poppy-crop|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿富汗地区由于常年战乱以及土地贫瘠，只能靠种植罂粟花生产毒品维持国民经济。過去[[泰國|泰國]]、[[寮國|寮國]]與[[緬甸|緬甸]]的[[國界|國界]]地區也是罂粟花产地，被稱為[[金三角|金三角]]<ref name="#1"/>。

中国的罂粟种植基地位于[[甘肃省|甘肃省]]，分布于[[甘肃农垦集团|甘肃农垦集团]]下属的部分农场。其中位于[[白银市|白银市]][[景泰县|景泰县]]的[[甘肃条山农工商（集团）有限责任公司|条山农场]]为唯一公开的罂粟种植基地。

